data.description: Super CLEAN property, shows like NEW! Great room with gas fireplace, vaulted ceiling and hardwood floors.  Formal Dining room, Beautiful Kitchen, with cherry cabinetry, black appliances and cut out window that looks into dining room. 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Baths, and Large Laundry Room.  Large Deck, Privacy Fence, and Brick Retaining Wall in backyard.
